{"tid":2241752,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"傳恒大擬折讓逾１１％配股，籌逾８０億元","createTime":"2020-10-13T13:57:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-14T16:37:03.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ceabef44352251b8bea984e63114d5885dcefd39","tid":2241752,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T13:57:52.000Z","msg":"《經濟通通訊社１３日專訊》據銷售文件披露，恆大（０３３３３）擬配售４﹒９億股，每<br />\n股作價１６﹒５元至１７﹒２元，較昨日收市價折讓１１﹒１％至１４﹒７％，集資額介乎<br />\n８０﹒８５億至８４﹒２８億元。<br />\n<br />\n  倘反應理想，可加碼１﹒２億股，合共配售最多６﹒１億股，合計集資額介乎１００﹒６５<br />\n億至１０４﹒９２億元。恆大是次配股集資所得用作現有債務再融資，以及一般營運資金。<br />\n（ｂｉ）"},{"pid":"2fb91d0075e1adf9bd8eb9087ce63bdc5986de65","tid":2241752,"uid":253016,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T14:00:13.000Z","msg":"邊個買廢紙"},{"pid":"e52a647ade87cd347ef91f8cc3d3e1f79a1c9a91","tid":2241752,"uid":243677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-13T14:01:20.000Z","msg":"收割散戶<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73fb4664d0d978a31e06831d00b8923e1e0647ed","tid":2241752,"uid":346701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T04:52:24.000Z","msg":"都只係夠還利息"},{"pid":"92bb5ad23b4ba64d7449770218c61189522e3f2b","tid":2241752,"uid":21592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73fb4664d0d978a31e06831d00b8923e1e0647ed","tid":2241752,"uid":346701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T04:52:24.000Z","msg":"都只係夠還利息"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T05:02:28.000Z","msg":"重點係港紙，還外債。"},{"pid":"d28d1ad65f16e094c6266877b61e695e9ec6e272","tid":2241752,"uid":138502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T05:06:43.000Z","msg":"現價 16.08 折條毛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04277a615bf7b264795caaff5924512a71699b85","tid":2241752,"uid":137493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T05:21:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0368c7d379bc305d595ada0